@startuml
object Teacher
object AuthController
object LinkTeacherDiscordUseCase
object CredentialStore
object TeacherWriter
object DiscordOAuth
Teacher --> AuthController : 1: request/link callback
AuthController --> LinkTeacherDiscordUseCase : 2: build/handle
LinkTeacherDiscordUseCase --> CredentialStore : 3: load client credential
LinkTeacherDiscordUseCase --> DiscordOAuth : 4: exchange code
LinkTeacherDiscordUseCase --> DiscordOAuth : 5: fetch user
LinkTeacherDiscordUseCase --> TeacherWriter : 6: load teacher
LinkTeacherDiscordUseCase --> TeacherWriter : 7: save discord id
LinkTeacherDiscordUseCase --> AuthController : 8: redirect url
AuthController --> Teacher : 9: redirect
@enduml
